lead_paragraph: The competition to replace Deshaun Watson at Clemson next spring will feature Kelly Bryant, who has already put two seasons of eligibility in behind the Tigers' star, along with redshirt freshman Zerrick Cooper and a five-star recruit who is enrolling in college early.

headline.main: Even for Contenders, Keeping QB Pipeline Filled Is Tricky
